    <div class="flexible-row">
        <div class="headerArea">
            <h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
            <p>@ViewBag.Message</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-container">
            <div class="flex-column">
                <img class="iconHeader" src="http://www.iconsdb.com/icons/preview/gray/pie-chart-xxl.png" />
                <div class="paper-bg headerHighlight">
                    <p>Portfolio management</p>
                </div>
                <div class="paper-bg-light subheaderHighlight">
                    <p>Why is it important?</p>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Portfolio management is all about finding the
                    optimal combination of stocks to have in your
                    portfolio.
                </p>
                <p>
                    By making sure that you have a well diversified
                    portfolio (i.e. spread your risks), you can ensure
                    that your returns will be both <u>higher</u> and <u>
                        more stable
                    </u> over time.
                </p>
                <p>
                    In practical terms, this means setting up
                    tools to monitor and guidelines like:
                </p>
                <ul class="ul-disc">
                    <li>Maximum weight of 10% in any single stock</li>
                    <li>Minimum of 4 different industries/sectors</li>
                    <li>Minimum of 2 different currencies</li>
                    <li>Minimum of 2 different countries</li>
                </ul>
                <br />
                <div class="paper-bg-light subheaderHighlight">
                    <p>Short-term Goals (TO-DO)</p>
                </div>
                <table class="adaptedTable">
                    <tr>
                        <td>1.</td>
                        <td>Create "Portfolio" page</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>2.</td>
                        <td>Create table: Portfolio summary</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>  </td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "Symbol"</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>  </td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "Name"</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>  </td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "Price"</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>  </td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "Currency"</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "# of shares"</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>  </td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "Value (SEK)"</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>  </td>
                        <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Add column "Weight (%)"</td>
                        <td><img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>3.</td>
                        <td>Create graph: Industry split</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>4.</td>
                        <td>Create graph: Currency split</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-space-column"></div>
            <div class="flex-column">
                <img class="iconHeader" src="https://maxcdn.icons8.com/iOS7/PNG/512/Business/bullish-512.png" />
                <div class="paper-bg headerHighlight">
                    <p>Stockpicking</p>
                </div>
                <div class="paper-bg-light subheaderHighlight">
                    <p>Why is it important?</p>
                </div>
                <p>
                    To be able to find the stocks which has a high
                    potential for stron returns, you need to to a
                    valuation of the companies on your "watchlist".
                </p>
                <p>
                    The result of your valuation will be a "target share
                    price", and by comparing this to the current share
                    price you can identify potential candidates for your
                    portfolio.
                </p>
                <p>
                    In practical terms, this includes:
                </p>
                <ul class="ul-disc">
                    <li>Analysing balance sheets</li>
                    <li>Analysing income statements</li>
                    <li>Analysing their business + products</li>
                    <li>Is it an area with large growth potential?</li>
                </ul>
                <br />
                <br />
                <div class="paper-bg-light subheaderHighlight">
                    <p>Short-term Goals (TO-DO)</p>
                </div>
                <table class="adaptedTable">
                    <tr>
                        <td>1.</td>
                        <td>Identify optimal data source</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>2.</td>
                        <td>Create SQL database</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>3.</td>
                        <td>Create "Screener"</td>
                        <td>@*<img class="miniIcon" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/haken.gif" />*@</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

